*.zwc
.zcompdump*

# Rice theme — `current` symlink is generated by theme-switch (points at the
# active theme); never commit it. App color blocks are stamped in-place by
# theme-switch but the committed files already carry the default theme, so they
# stay tracked.
linux/theme/current

# Noctalia — colors.json is regenerated from the active wallpaper, so it churns
# on every wallpaper change. settings.json + colorschemes stay tracked.
linux/noctalia/colors.json
